75
00:03:00,300 --> 00:03:01,380
and very rigorous research

76
00:03:01,380 --> 00:03:03,450
in the realm of visual neuroscience.

77
00:03:03,450 --> 00:03:04,710
And in the last decade or so,

78
00:03:04,710 --> 00:03:07,020
they turned their attention
to exploring the role

79
00:03:07,020 --> 00:03:11,780
