into electrical signals

93
00:03:39,230 --> 00:03:41,050
that the rest of the brain can understand

94
00:03:41,050 --> 00:03:42,840
and create visual images from,

95
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:46,060
well, those cells are
extremely metabolically active.

96
00:03:46,060 --> 00:03:49,870
They need a lot of ATP or energy.

97
00:03:49,870 --> 00:03:51,390
And as we age,

98
00:03:51,390 --> 00:03:53,570
those cells get less efficient

99
00:03:53,570 --> 00:03:56,370
at creating that ATP and energy.

100
00:03:56,370 --> 00:03:58,990
Exposure to red light early in the day,

101
00:03:58,990 --> 00:04:01,090
and it does have to be early in the day,

102
00:04:01,090 --> 00:04:03,960
