01:12:59,410 --> 01:13:03,190
you are going to get far
more light energy, photons

1786
01:13:03,190 --> 01:13:06,670
through cloud cover than
you are going to get

1787
01:13:06,670 --> 01:13:10,180
from an indoor light source,
an artificial light source.

1788
01:13:10,180 --> 01:13:12,730
I can't emphasize this enough.

1789
01:13:12,730 --> 01:13:14,090
If you look outside in the morning

1790
01:13:14,090 --> 01:13:16,130
and you see some sunlight,

1791
01:13:16,130 --> 01:13:17,780
if you see some sunlight
throughout the day,

1792
01:13:17,780 --> 01:13:20,410
you would do yourself a great favor

1793
01:13:20,410 --> 01:13:22,140
to try and chase some of that sunlight

1794
01:13:22,140 --> 01:13:25,130
and get into that sunlight
to expose your eyes

1795
01:13:25,130 --> 01:13:28,170
and your skin to that sunlight
