1796
01:13:28,170 --> 01:13:30,610
And when I say as much as you safely can,

1797
01:13:30,610 --> 01:13:31,940
never ever look at any light,

1798
01:13:31,940 --> 01:13:33,670
artificial, sunlight, or otherwise,

1799
01:13:33,670 --> 01:13:35,340
that's so bright that
