but I've described one before
and I'll describe it again.

1885
01:17:03,720 --> 01:17:06,160
And we can provide a link to
a couple examples of these

1886
01:17:06,160 --> 01:17:09,450
in the show, in the show
note captions, excuse me.

1887
01:17:09,450 --> 01:17:14,450
This is a 930 to 1,000
lux, L-U-X, light source

1888
01:17:14,840 --> 01:17:16,400
that's designed for drawing.

