1892
01:17:22,730 --> 01:17:23,563
I actually have one,

1893
01:17:23,563 --> 01:17:25,550
and I position it on my desk all day long.

1894
01:17:25,550 --> 01:17:27,780
I also happen to have
skylights above my desk.

1895
01:17:27,780 --> 01:17:29,910
I'm fairly sensitive to
the effects of light.

1896
01:17:29,910 --> 01:17:31,290
So in longer days I feel much better

1897
01:17:31,290 --> 01:17:32,230
than I do in shorter days.

1898
01:17:32,230 --> 01:17:33,150
I've never suffered

1899
01:17:33,150 --> 01:17:35,180
from full-blown seasonal
effective disorder,

1900
01:17:35,180 --> 01:17:38,730
but I keep that light
source on throughout the day

1901
01:17:38,730 --> 01:17:39,690
throughout the year.

1902
01:17:39,690 --> 01:17:42,110
But I also make it a point to
get outside and get sunlight

1903
01:17:42,110 --> 01:17:44,550
early in the morning and several
times throughout the day.

1904
01:17:44,550 --> 01:17:47,270
And if it's particularly overcast outside

1905
01:17:47,270 --> 01:17:49,670
or there just doesn't seem
to be a lot of sunlight

1906
01:17:49,670 --> 01:17:50,960
coming through those clouds,

1907
01:17:50,960 --> 01:17:53,540
I will try to look at that light source

1908
01:17:53,540 --> 01:17:54,880
a little bit more each day

1909
01:17:54,880 --> 01:17:57,420
in order to trigger these mechanisms.

1910
01:17:57,420 --> 01:18:00,160
Now, some people may
desire to get UVB exposure

1911
01:18:00,160 --> 01:18:02,160
to their skin and they want to do that

1912
01:18:02,160 --> 01:18:03,920
through sources other than sunlight.

1913
01:18:03,920 --> 01:18:06,150
And there it's a little
bit more complicated.

1914
01:18:06,150 --> 01:18:08,330
There are, of course, tanning salons,

1915
01:18:08,330 --> 01:18:10,700
which basically are beds of UVB light.

1916
01:18:10,700 --> 01:18:12,160
That's really all they are.

1917
01:18:12,160 --> 01:18:13,130
I've never been to one.

1918
01:18:13,130 --> 01:18:14,630
I know people do frequent them

1919
01:18:14,630 --> 01:18:16,130
in certain parts of the world.

1920
01:18:17,070 --> 01:18:19,320
There, of course, people
are covering their eyes.

1921
01:18:19,320 --> 01:18:21,780
They are only getting UVB
exposure to their skin, typically

1922
01:18:21,780 --> 01:18:24,920
because the UVB exposure,
or intensities rather,

1923
01:18:24,920 --> 01:18:26,560
tend to be very, very high.

1924
01:18:26,560 --> 01:18:27,920
And so you can actually damage your eyes.

1925
01:18:27,920 --> 01:18:29,940
If you're looking at a very, very bright

1926
01:18:29,940 --> 01:18:32,530
artificial UVB source up close.

1927
01:18:32,530 --> 01:18:35,190
So you really have to explore
these options for yourself.

1928
01:18:35,190 --> 01:18:37,150
Sunlight of course, being the original

1929
01:18:37,150 --> 01:18:40,780
and still the best way
to get UVB exposure.

1930
01:18:40,780 --> 01:18:44,510
So without knowing your particular
circumstances, finances,

1931
01:18:44,510 --> 01:18:47,390
genetics, or place of origin, et cetera,

1932
01:18:47,390 --> 01:18:48,590
I can't know whether or not

1933
01:18:48,590 --> 01:18:49,890
you need to use artificial sources.

1934
01:18:49,890 --> 01:18:51,650
You're going to have to gauge that.

1935
01:18:51,650 --> 01:18:55,250
Meanwhile, getting outside, looking at

1936
01:18:55,250 --> 01:18:59,330
and getting some exposure
of UVB onto your skin

1937
01:18:59,330 --> 01:19:00,550
is going to be beneficial

1938
01:19:00,550 --> 01:19:03,380
for the vast majority of people out there.

1939
01:19:03,380 --> 01:19:05,530
And in fact, it's even
going to be beneficial

1940
01:19:05,530 --> 01:19:07,123
for people that are blind.

1941
01:19:08,130 --> 01:19:10,770
People that are blind,
provided they still have eyes,

1942
01:19:10,770 --> 01:19:14,230
often maintain these melanopsin cells.

1943
01:19:14,230 --> 01:19:16,240
So even if you're low vision or no vision,

1944
01:19:16,240 --> 01:19:18,110
getting UVB exposure to your eyes

1945
01:19:18,110 --> 01:19:21,060
can be very beneficial for sake of mood,

1946
01:19:21,060 --> 01:19:24,400
hormone pathways, pain
reduction, and so forth.

1947
01:19:24,400 --> 01:19:28,820
A cautionary note, people who
have retinitis pigmentosa,

1948
01:19:28,820 --> 01:19:31,390
macular degeneration, or glaucoma,

1949
01:19:31,390 --> 01:19:34,730
as well as people who are
especially prone to skin cancers

1950
01:19:34,730 --> 01:19:37,660
should definitely consult
with your ophthalmologist

1951
01:19:37,660 --> 01:19:40,130
and dermatologist before
you start increasing

1952
01:19:40,130 --> 01:19:41,970
the total amount of UVB exposure

1953
01:19:41,970 --> 01:19:44,990
that you're getting from any
source, sunlight or otherwise.

1954
01:19:44,990 --> 01:19:47,780
There are additional, very
interesting and powerful effects

1955
01:19:47,780 --> 01:19:52,483
of UVB light, in particular
on immune function.

1956
01:19:54,060 --> 01:19:57,330
All the organs of our
body are inside our skin.

1957
01:19:57,330 --> 01:20:00,500
And so information about
external conditions,

1958
01:20:00,500 --> 01:20:02,250
meaning the environment that we're in,

1959
01:20:02,250 --> 01:20:06,410
need to be communicated to the
various organs of our body.

1960
01:20:06,410 --> 01:20:08,700
Some of them have more direct access

1961
01:20:08,700 --> 01:20:10,630
to what's going on outside.

1962
01:20:10,630 --> 01:20:13,830
So for instance, the cells in your brain

1963
01:20:13,830 --> 01:20:15,640
that reside right over
the roof of your mouth,

1964
01:20:15,640 --> 01:20:17,468
your hypothalamus, they
control hormone output,

1965
01:20:17,468 --> 01:20:20,600
and they control the biological functions

1966
01:20:20,600 --> 01:20:21,980
that we call circadian functions,

1967
01:20:21,980 --> 01:20:24,470
the ones that change every 24 hours.

1968
01:20:24,470 --> 01:20:27,100
Well, those are just
one or two connections,

1969
01:20:27,100 --> 01:20:29,800
meaning synapses away from
those cells in your eye

1970
01:20:29,800 --> 01:20:32,563
that perceive UB, UVB light, excuse me.

1971
01:20:33,440 --> 01:20:36,010
Other organs of your
body, such as your spleen,

1972
01:20:36,010 --> 01:20:38,920
which is involved in the
creation of molecules

1973
01:20:38,920 --> 01:20:41,260
and cells that combat infection,

1974
01:20:41,260 --> 01:20:42,990
well, those are a long ways away

1975
01:20:42,990 --> 01:20:43,823
from those cell in your eye.

1976
01:20:43,823 --> 01:20:47,280
And in fact, they're a long
ways away from your skin.

1977
01:20:47,280 --> 01:20:48,940
There are beautiful studies showing

1978
01:20:48,940 --> 01:20:53,260
that if we get more UVB
exposure from sunlight

1979
01:20:53,260 --> 01:20:55,993
or from appropriate artificial sources,

1980
01:20:57,260 --> 01:21:00,830
that spleen and immune
function are enhanced,

1981
01:21:00,830 --> 01:21:03,160
and there's a very logical,

1982
01:21:03,160 --> 01:21:06,070
well-established circuit
as to how that happens.

1983
01:21:06,070 --> 01:21:09,350
Your brain actually
connects to your spleen.

1984
01:21:09,350 --> 01:21:12,047
Now, it's not the case
that you can simply think,

1985
01:21:12,047 --> 01:21:14,720
"Okay, spleen, turn on,
release killer cells,

1986
01:21:14,720 --> 01:21:16,410
go out and combat infection."

1987
01:21:16,410 --> 01:21:20,730
However, UVB light arriving on the eyes

1988
01:21:20,730 --> 01:21:23,560
is known to trigger
activation of the neurons

1989
01:21:23,560 --> 01:21:26,070
within the so-called
sympathetic nervous system.

1990
01:21:26,070 --> 01:21:28,400
These neurons are part of the larger thing

1991
01:21:28,400 --> 01:21:30,140
that we call the autonomic nervous system,

1992
01:21:30,140 --> 01:21:34,210
meaning it's below or not
accessible by conscious control.

1993
01:21:34,210 --> 01:21:35,590
It's the thing that
controls your heartbeat,

1994
01:21:35,590 --> 01:21:38,060
controls your breathing
and that also activates

1995
01:21:38,060 --> 01:21:41,040
or flips on the switch
of your immune system.

1996
01:21:41,040 --> 01:21:43,600
When we get a lot of
UVB light in our eyes,

1997
01:21:43,600 --> 01:21:46,900
or I should say sufficient
UVB light in our eyes,

1998
01:21:46,900 --> 01:21:50,150
a particular channel, a
particular set of connections

1999
01:21:50,150 --> 01:21:53,260
within the sympathetic
nervous system is activated,

2000
01:21:53,260 --> 01:21:57,380
and our spleen deploys
immune cells and molecules

2001
01:21:57,380 --> 01:22:00,330
that scavenge for and combat infection.

2002
01:22:00,330 --> 01:22:03,900
So if you've noticed that
you get fewer colds and flus

2003
01:22:03,900 --> 01:22:06,830
and other forms of illness
in the summer months,

2004
01:22:06,830 --> 01:22:10,470
part of that could be because
of the increase in temperature

2005
01:22:10,470 --> 01:22:11,303
in your environment,

2006
01:22:11,303 --> 01:22:13,310
because typically longer
days are associated

2007
01:22:13,310 --> 01:22:15,660
with more warmth in your environment

2008
01:22:15,660 --> 01:22:16,850
as opposed to winter days,

2009
01:22:16,850 --> 01:22:19,590
which are short when it
tends to be colder out.

2010
01:22:19,590 --> 01:22:24,000
Well, that's true, but it's also the case

2011
01:22:24,000 --> 01:22:26,480
that people around you
have fewer colds and flus

2012
01:22:26,480 --> 01:22:29,680
and that you will get infected
with fewer colds and flus

2013
01:22:29,680 --> 01:22:34,520
and other infections,
because if those infections,

2014
01:22:34,520 --> 01:22:36,940
whether or not they're bacterial or viral,

2015
01:22:36,940 --> 01:22:39,430
arrive in your body,
right, if you inhale them

2016
01:22:39,430 --> 01:22:42,000
or they get into your
mouth or on your skin,

2017
01:22:42,000 --> 01:22:45,550
your spleen meets those
infections with a greater output.

2018
01:22:45,550 --> 01:22:47,580
In other words, the soldiers
of your immune system,

2019
01:22:47,580 --> 01:22:50,240
the chemicals and cell
types of your immune system

2020
01:22:50,240 --> 01:22:52,150
that combat infection

2021
01:22:52,150 --> 01:22:56,490
are in a more ready,
deployed stance, if you will.

2022
01:22:56,490 --> 01:22:58,210
If you want to know more
about the immune system

2023
01:22:58,210 --> 01:22:59,070
and immune function,

2024
