We talk about cytokines,

2027
01:23:05,950 --> 01:23:08,060
we talk about killer cells,
B cells, T cells, et cetera,

2028
01:23:08,060 --> 01:23:09,540
a lot of detail there.

2029
01:23:09,540 --> 01:23:11,760
So we often think about the summer months

2030
01:23:11,760 --> 01:23:15,350
and the spring months as fewer
infections floating around.

2031
01:23:15,350 --> 01:23:18,890
But in fact, there aren't fewer
infections floating around.

