2661
01:49:32,920 --> 01:49:35,210
of the episode from Dr. Glen Jeffery

2662
01:49:35,210 --> 01:49:37,070
at University College London,

2663
01:49:37,070 --> 01:49:40,620
who, again, is a longstanding member

2664
01:49:40,620 --> 01:49:41,710
of the neuroscience community,

2665
01:49:41,710 --> 01:49:43,260
working on visual neuroscience,

2666
01:49:43,260 --> 01:49:45,450
and who over the last decade or so

2667
01:49:45,450 --> 01:49:48,570
has really emphasized the
exploration of red light

2668
01:49:48,570 --> 01:49:51,550
and near-infrared light for restoration

2669
01:49:51,550 --> 01:49:54,020
