2857
01:57:58,090 --> 01:57:59,910
as a sense to navigate
the world and survive.

2858
01:57:59,910 --> 01:58:01,270
So this is really wonderful.

2859
01:58:01,270 --> 01:58:03,070
Here, we're looking at a therapy

2860
01:58:03,070 --> 01:58:06,580
