2873
01:58:35,940 --> 01:58:38,200
One of the things that they observed was

2874
01:58:38,200 --> 01:58:41,780
a reduction in so-called
drusen, D-R-U-S-E-N.

2875
01:58:41,780 --> 01:58:45,770
Drusen are little fatty deposits,

2876
01:58:45,770 --> 01:58:47,470
little cholesterol deposits,

2877
01:58:47,470 --> 01:58:49,920
that accumulate in the eye as we age.

2878
01:58:49,920 --> 01:58:51,580
We've all heard about cholesterol

2879
01:58:51,580 --> 01:58:53,130
within our veins and arteries

2880
01:58:53,130 --> 01:58:55,690
and how that can clog
our veins and arteries

2881
01:58:55,690 --> 01:58:58,760
and how, of course, clogging
of veins and arteries

2882
01:58:58,760 --> 01:58:59,790
is not a good thing.

2883
01:58:59,790 --> 01:59:02,580
Well, our neural retina
being so metabolically active

2884
01:59:02,580 --> 01:59:04,170
requires a lot of blood flow.

2885
01:59:04,170 --> 01:59:06,180
It's heavily vascularized,

2886
01:59:06,180 --> 01:59:09,120
and drusen are a special
form of cholesterol

2887
01:59:09,120 --> 01:59:11,300
that accumulate in the eye.

2888
01:59:11,300 --> 01:59:12,930
As it turns out, these red light

2889
01:59:12,930 --> 01:59:15,060
and near-infrared light therapies

2890
01:59:15,060 --> 01:59:16,500
explored by the Jeffery Lab

2891
01:59:16,500 --> 01:59:19,610
were able to actually reduce or reverse

2892
01:59:19,610 --> 01:59:21,630
some of the accumulation of drusen.

2893
01:59:21,630 --> 01:59:25,670
And so in addition to reducing
reactive oxygen species,

2894
01:59:25,670 --> 01:59:28,010
the idea in mind now is that red light

2895
01:59:28,010 --> 01:59:31,560
may actually reduce cholesterol deposits

2896
01:59:31,560 --> 01:59:34,120
and reactive oxygen species

2897
01:59:34,120 --> 01:59:36,560
in order to improve neuronal function.

2898
01:59:36,560 --> 01:59:38,760
So what should you and
