2945
02:01:23,550 --> 02:01:25,510
or you could purchase a red light unit

2946
02:01:25,510 --> 02:01:27,470
if that was within your budget

2947
02:01:27,470 --> 02:01:29,000
and something that you're interested in.

2948
02:01:29,000 --> 02:01:30,840
You want to make sure
