2956
02:01:43,050 --> 02:01:44,910
that means it's too bright to look at

2957
02:01:44,910 --> 02:01:46,020
without closing your eyes.

2958
02:01:46,020 --> 02:01:47,420
Okay, that's sort of a duh,

2959
02:01:47,420 --> 02:01:48,960
but I would loathe to think

2960
02:01:48,960 --> 02:01:50,420
that anyone would harm themselves

2961
02:01:50,420 --> 02:01:51,770
with bright light in any way.

2962
02:01:51,770 --> 02:01:52,980
I don't just say that to protect us.

2963
02:01:52,980 --> 02:01:54,870
I say that to protect you, of course,

2964
02:01:54,870 --> 02:01:56,730
because you are responsible
for your health.

2965
02:01:56,730 --> 02:01:59,320
And again, retinal
neurons do not regenerate.

2966
02:01:59,320 --> 02:02:02,170
Once they are gone and
dead, they do not come back.

2967
02:02:02,170 --> 02:02:03,780
There's no technology to replace them

2968
02:02:03,780 --> 02:02:06,270
at this current state in time.

2969
02:02:06,270 --> 02:02:08,400
So please don't damage your retinas.

2970
02:02:08,400 --> 02:02:10,870
So is a red light source safe to look at

2971
02:02:10,870 --> 02:02:13,500
if it is not painful to look at?

2972
02:02:13,500 --> 02:02:14,580
