2977
02:02:23,230 --> 02:02:25,050
to pursue the sorts of protocols

2978
02:02:25,050 --> 02:02:26,270
that are in the Jeffery studies,

2979
02:02:26,270 --> 02:02:28,450
certainly we'll provide
a link to those studies.

2980
02:02:28,450 --> 02:02:31,170
Again, it involved looking
at these red light panels,

2981
